# Cursor IDE Rules

## Pre-open Files on Session Start

These files should be opened automatically when starting a new Cursor session to provide immediate context:

- docs/architecture/tldr.md
- docs/roadmap/phase1_milestones.md  
- docs/contracts/trade_v1.md
- docs/journal/now.md
- docs/handbook-mount/README.md

## File Priority

High-signal documentation for quick reference and planning:
1. Current status (journal/now.md)
2. Architecture overview (architecture/tldr.md)
3. Development roadmap (roadmap/phase1_milestones.md)
4. API contracts (contracts/trade_v1.md)
5. External documentation mount point (handbook-mount/README.md)
